items.Video_Title: Last minute GLOW-UP for school pt.2 #shoppinghaul #clothinghaul #shorts #glowup #backtoschool
I Bought The Same Dress For $4, $30, $60, and $200
items.Video_Description:
HELLO FRIENDS!! So, I found something... a few months ago, while we were trying to film a video where I let TikTok ads pick my outfits, I stumbled upon... this dress. It goes by a few names but it's most commonly some version of the "floral midriff shaper corset sundress" - and after buying one for the video, my for you page started getting flooded with TONS of ads for what looked like the same dress - but all from different companies, and with wildly different price points. So, I decided - let's buy a few of these bad boys and see what actually ends up at our doorstep - and find out, what the heck IS up. Where are all these dresses coming from? Are they all the same dress? Clearly someone is lying here - but who? I guess we'll find out...

This video is NOT sponsored!!

items.Video_Title: Let’s talk 'Haul Culture'.
items.Video_Description:
Another day, another haul 🛍️👀 Try Rocket Money for free: https://RocketMoney.com/CARA  #rocketmoney #personalfinance

🎥  More about this video: 
We see it everywhere on social media - bags and boxes galore of products, typically clothes but sometimes gadgets, tech, beauty, or something else all together. People spending hundreds of dollars at a time on their purchases. Haul culture has only become more popular in the age of short-form videos on TikTok or Reels, microtrends from fashion houses, and industries like fast fashion that prioritize quantity over quality. So what does our insatiable desire for watching and making hauls come from? Let's talk the psychology behind our haul obsession on social media, how it impacts our planet and our finances, and what steps you can take to move away from haul culture.

Want more videos on money, media, society, and intentional living? Be sure to subscribe for more video essays!

@amandamaryanna 's video on the history of hauls: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RflFqSqMPX4
